ucted from repeated cross-sectional surveys for poverty trend analysis. This would provide more coverage of poverty over time as this type of data are more readily available, but still only looking at average welfare for groups, not households.", "start_char_idx": null, "end_char_idx": null, "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_seperator": "\n"}, "__type__": "1"}, "92d2cbf6-a057-4e76-8e33-c73252353be6": {"__data__": {"id_": "92d2cbf6-a057-4e76-8e33-c73252353be6", "embedding": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/assessing-relationship-between-natural-hazards-and-poverty-conceptual-and-methodological-proposal", "Author": "United Nations Development Programme", "Publisher": "United Nations Development Programme", "Type": "Report"}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "Assessing the Relationship between Natural Hazards and Poverty \u2013 A Conceptual and Methodological Proposal", "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/assessing-relationship-between-natural-hazards-and-poverty-conceptual-and-methodological-proposal", "Author": "United Nations Development Programme", "Publisher": "United Nations Development Programme", "Type": "Report"}, "hash": "d2b480d2367c3828462733c4c934da55ebdf15240286956433ab1ef79702130f"}, "2": {"node_id": "4078ef95-208a-4734-bc18-60d0f0e0b9f3", "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/assessing-relationship-between-natural-hazards-and-poverty-conceptual-and-methodological-proposal", "Author": "United Nations Development Programme", "Publisher": "United Nations Development Programme", "Type": "Report"}, "hash": "4872a779de88c36967297e9e7e16bd998e480e4b92c0951775183270004e6fab"}}, "hash": "ce90b6e1a71847c6d10d2e45771932e8645032de806bc42712a41699957475f4", "text": "Obviously, 